  "title": "feat(API): new export strategy",
  "body": "feat(API): new export strategy\n\nBREAKING CHANGE: The way to access connectors (NameOfWidget.connect)\nand default widgets (NameOfWidget) has changed. You need to update\nyour imports.\n\nNow:\n\n``` js\nimport {InstantSearch, SearchBox, RangeRatings} from 'react-instantsearch/dom';\nimport {connectSearchBox} from 'react-instantsearch/connectors';\nimport {createConnector} from 'react-instantsearch';\n```\n\nBefore:\n\n``` js\nimport {InstantSearch, SearchBox, Range} from 'react-instantsearch/dom';\n// use SearchBox.connect\n// use Range.Ratings\n```\n\nfixes #1454\n\nUltimately we might have different packages. This will also ease usage\nin react-native moving forward.\n",
